%md-dialog{style: "width: 50%;"}
  %md-toolbar.md-accent
    %div.md-toolbar-tools
      Help keep Chutter.co online
      %span{flex: true}
      %md-button.md-icon-button{ng-click: "hideDialog()"}
        %i.fa.fa-close.fa-fw{aria-label="Close dialog"}
  %md-dialog-content{ng-if: "false"}
    %section#subscription-section
      %md-list
        %md-list-item.md-2-line
          %md-icon{layout: "row", layout-align: "center center"}
            %i.icon.ion-ribbon-a
          .md-list-item-text
            %h3 Gild up to 10 users a month
            %p Award the best comments / posts and the user gets a free month of chutter pro.
        %md-list-item.md-2-line
          %md-icon{layout: "row", md-svg-src: "/img/character.svg"}
          .md-list-item-text
            %h3 Support Chutter
            %p You can pay for a meaningful chunk of server time for only 4 quarters a month.

        %md-list-item.md-2-line
          %md-icon{layout: "row", layout-align: "center center"}
            %i.icon.ion-android-notifications-off
          .md-list-item-text
            %h3 Mute post / comment notifications
            %p No more "R.I.P inbox". Easily mute comment / post / message notifications
        %md-list-item.md-2-line
          %md-icon{layout: "row", layout-align: "center center"}
            %i.icon.ion-android-funnel
          .md-list-item-text
            %h3 Saved categories
            %p All of your saved posts will automatically be categorized (e.g. "music", "videos", etc...).
  %md-dialog-content
    %p
      Chutter costs quite a bit to run, donations are currently the only way we have to pay for server costs! Your donations will immediately support server costs, mobile app development and allow chutter to grow into something big.  
    <form action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post" target="_top">
      <input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick">
      <input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="9DHHFNE2GQCTG">
      <input type="image" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_donate_SM.gif" border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!">
      <img alt="" border="0" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif" width="1" height="1">
    </form>



